15namespace webrtc {
16
17RtcEventAudioPlayout::RtcEventAudioPlayout(uint32_t ssrc) : ssrc_(ssrc) {}
18
19RtcEventAudioPlayout::RtcEventAudioPlayout(const RtcEventAudioPlayout& other)
20 : RtcEvent(other.timestamp_us_), ssrc_(other.ssrc_) {}
21
22std::unique_ptr<RtcEventAudioPlayout> RtcEventAudioPlayout::Copy() const {
23 return absl::WrapUnique<RtcEventAudioPlayout>(
24 new RtcEventAudioPlayout(*this));
25}
